{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781721915125,"sessionID":"ses_1291f676affeVoh3Pb0kJSjTck","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"tool_kV30cewnyJoNFuxBWjlHgC9A","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Deep Review Dashboard\n\n*Auto-generated; do not edit manually.*\n\n## Status\n\n- Iteration: 1 of 1 (complete)\n- Provisional verdict: **CONDITIONAL**\n- hasAdvisories: true\n- Stop reason: maxIterations reached\n\n## Findings Summary\n\n| Severity | Count | Delta |\n|----------|-------|-------|\n| P0 | 0 | +0 |\n| P1 | 2 | +2 |\n| P2 | 2 | +2 |\n\n## Dimension Coverage\n\n| Dimension | Covered | Iteration |\n|-----------|---------|-----------|\n| correctness | yes | 1 |\n| security | no | вҖ” |\n| traceability | yes | 1 |\n| maintainability | no | вҖ” |\n\n## Progress\n\n| Run | Status | Focus | Dimensions | New Findings Ratio | Findings |\n|-----|--------|-------|------------|-------------------|----------|\n| 1 | complete | correctness | correctness, traceability | 0.57 | 0 P0, 2 P1, 2 P2 |\n\n## Next Focus\n\nIteration budget exhausted. Proceed to synthesis.\n\n## Active Risks\n\n- Two unaddressed P1 findings block a PASS verdict.\n- Security and maintainability dimensions were not covered due to maxIterations=1.\n- No blocked-stop events recorded.\n","filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/review/lineages/p020-kimi-2/deep-review-dashboard.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/review/lineages/p020-kimi-2/deep-review-dashboard.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/review/lineages/p020-kimi-2/deep-review-dashboard.md